{
  "stem": "9878.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I saw two big streams of blood, maybe three or four feet high, coming out of his throat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the dog killed him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he called him back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was nearly-- I was out of my mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I started-- I tried to start running.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was shocked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I couldn't ran.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I couldn't do-- I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I saw the way he called the dog back, and he petted the dog.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He bent down, something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't if he kissed him or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then he took something out of his pocket to give to the dog.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The [INAUDIBLE] one of our prophecies, and I forgot their names, that they said there will come a day that the men would not have pity at the suckling-- a baby suckling milk with his mother-- or an old man with a gray beard.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They'll kill-- kiss the calf and kiss the dog.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "This prophecy was what come-- come true.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I start running any time, even in America.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "When I pass by the car door and I see a man come with a big dog, and I get scared.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "My heart starts pumping to me, because it's with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I will see the picture of one [INAUDIBLE] till the day I die.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The way a dog is capable of saving a man, a German dog, if he's taught.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he's capable of killing a  man in seconds, in minutes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He just ripped his throat apart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I never believed a dog could do such things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And then I'll tell you an incident maybe it happened after this incident.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "There's another incident where the Germans gave an order the Jewish people cannot go to the river because the river passed the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
